<Layout title="Privacy Policy | TaskRocket" description="TaskRocket privacy policy and SMS privacy disclosures.">
  <section class="legal"><div class="container"><article><h1>Privacy Policy</h1><p>Last updated: May 2026</p><p>TaskRocket collects information you choose to provide when you request a workflow review, contact us, or use our services.</p><h2>Information We Collect</h2><ul><li>Contact information such as name, business name, email address, phone number, and mailing address if provided.</li><li>Form submissions and details about the workflow or service you ask us to review.</li><li>SMS consent status and related communication records if you opt in to text messages.</li><li>Message history, scheduling details, and service-related notes when needed to support your inquiry or account.</li></ul><h2>How We Use Information</h2><p>We use information to respond to inquiries, provide workflow reviews, schedule demos or consultations, deliver services, maintain records, improve our operations, and communicate with you about TaskRocket services.</p><h2>SMS Communication</h2><p>SMS consent and phone numbers collected for SMS communication are used only for TaskRocket communication related to inquiries, workflow reviews, demo requests, scheduling, service updates, and account communication. SMS consent is not sold, rented, or shared with third parties for their marketing purposes.</p><h2>Sharing Information</h2><p>We do not sell personal information. We may use service providers to operate our website, forms, messaging, scheduling, email, hosting, analytics, and business systems. These providers are used only to support TaskRocket operations.</p><h2>Data Retention</h2><p>We retain information as long as reasonably needed for business, legal, operational, and service purposes.</p><h2>Your Choices</h2><p>You may request updates or deletion of your information by contacting TaskRocket. If you opted in to SMS, reply STOP to unsubscribe or HELP for help.</p><h2>Contact</h2><p>TaskRocket<br/>Website: taskrocket.org<br/>Email: info@taskrocket.org<br/>Phone: 252-205-4287<br/>Mailing address: 217 S. Goldsboro St. Wilson NC 27893</p></article></div></section>
</Layout>
